OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FBritish nationals are among the
OL,8,Fhundreds of thousands of travellers
OL,9,Fstranded in Gulf Arab states, as major
OL,10,Fairports, including Dubai, remained
OL,11,Fclosed following retaliatory strikes
OL,12,Ffrom Iran.
OL,14,FIran fired missiles at its Gulf
OL,15,Fneighbours after the US and Israel
OL,16,Flaunched airstrikes on major cities,
OL,17,Fincluding the capital, Tehran on
OL,18,FSaturday. Iran's Supreme Leader, Ali
OL,19,FKhamenei, was later confirmed to have
OL,20,Fdied in the assault.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
