PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772467872
OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FThe disruption continued into Sunday
OL,8,Fas Iran launched fresh strikes on the
OL,9,Fregion, with major airlines suspending
OL,10,Fflights until Monday.
OL,12,FDubai is a popular holiday destination
OL,13,Ffor Brits and there are thousands of
OL,14,FBritish expats in the UAE.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772467872
OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FBritish holidaymakers who were locked
OL,8,Fdown in their hotels told ITV News
OL,9,Fthat the situation was "terrifying".
OL,10,FKirsty Greyling is on holiday in Dubai
OL,11,Fwith her toddler and said the "vibe
OL,12,Fwas quite fraught" in the city. She
OL,13,Fhad been sitting in a restaurant
OL,14,Fopposite Dubai's famous Fairmont The
OL,15,FPalm Hotel when it was hit following
OL,16,Fretaliatory strikes by Iran.
OL,18,FThey slept in the basement of their
OL,19,Fhotel overnight and are now waiting to
OL,20,Ffind out when they can be rebooked on
OL,21,Fa flight home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772467872
OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,F"The vibe is fraught but we do feel
OL,8,Fsafe inside the hotel," she told ITV
OL,9,FNews.
OL,11,F"We can't go outside the hotel... you
OL,12,Fcan hear the odd missile in the
OL,13,Fbackground."
OL,15,FIn a statement published on X on
OL,16,FSunday morning, Emirates airline said:
OL,17,F"Due to multiple regional airspace
OL,18,Fclosures, Emirates has temporarily
OL,19,Fsuspended all operations to and from
OL,20,FDubai, up until 3pm UAE time on Monday
OL,21,FMarch 2."
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
