OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772467872
OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FThe airline has advised passengers
OL,8,Fbooked to travel before or on March 5
OL,9,Fto rebook on an alternate flight, or
OL,10,Frequest a refund.
OL,12,FEtihad Airways advised passengers that
OL,13,Fwhile airspace closures continue,
OL,14,Fdisruption is to be expected.
OL,16,F"Regional airspace closures continue
OL,17,Fto impact Etihad's operations, and all
OL,18,Fflights to and from Abu Dhabi are
OL,19,Fsuspended until 2am UAE time on Monday
OL,20,FMarch 2," the airline said on X.
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
