OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772467872
OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FEtihad said passengers should check
OL,8,Ftheir flight status on its website
OL,9,Fbefore travelling to the airport and
OL,10,Fensure their contact details are up to
OL,11,Fdate in their booking.
OL,13,FPeople holding Etihad tickets for
OL,14,Ftravel on dates up to March 3 can also
OL,15,Frequest a full refund, the airline
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FQatar Airways said on Saturday night
OL,19,Fthat flights remained temporarily
OL,20,Fsuspended due to the closure of Qatari
OL,21,Fairspace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
