OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772467872
OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FThere are still 83 flights scheduled
OL,8,Fto operate between the UK and the
OL,9,FMiddle East on Sunday, according to
OL,10,Faviation analytics company Cirium.
OL,12,FThe Foreign Office has advised British
OL,13,Fnationals in Bahrain, Israel,
OL,14,FPalestine, Qatar and United Arab
OL,15,FEmirates to register their presence
OL,16,Fwith the UK Government to receive
OL,17,Fupdates on the situation in the Middle
OL,18,FEast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
