OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772467872
OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FIn a statement published on X on
OL,8,FSaturday night, the Foreign,
OL,9,FCommonwealth and Development Office
OL,10,F(FCDO) said: "British nationals in
OL,11,FBahrain, Israel, Palestine, Qatar and
OL,12,FUnited Arab Emirates can register
OL,13,Ftheir presence to receive direct
OL,14,Fupdates from the FCDO on the situation
OL,15,Fin the Middle East.
OL,17,F"You should continue to follow travel
OL,18,Fadvice and the advice of the local
OL,19,Fauthorities."
OL,26,@rD@NOUyD@AOU{D@MO]
