OL,3,CBritons among thousands stranded in
OL,4,CDubai as flights across Middle East
OL,5,Cgrounded
OL,7,FFour people were injured at Dubai
OL,8,FInternational Airport, the largest in
OL,9,Fthe United Arab Emirates and one of
OL,10,Fthe busiest in the world, on Saturday
OL,11,Fafter what the UAE government called a
OL,12,F"blatant attack involving Iranian
OL,13,Fballistic missiles.
OL,15,FWhile Zayed International Airport in
OL,16,FAbu Dhabi said that one person was
OL,17,Fkilled and seven others were injured
OL,18,Fin a drone strike. Strikes were also
OL,19,Freported at Kuwait International
OL,20,FAirport.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
